âœ… What are Semantic Tags in HTML?
Semantic tags are HTML elements that clearly describe their meaning and purpose to both the browser and developers.
They make the code more readable, accessible, and SEO-friendly.

ğŸ”¹ Examples of Semantic Tags
<header> â€“ Top section of a page or section
