ğŸ¨ CSS NOTES (Quick & Clear)
ğŸ”¹ What is CSS?
CSS (Cascading Style Sheets) is used to style and layout web pagesâ€”colors, fonts, spacing, positioning, and responsiveness.

ğŸ”¹ Ways to Apply CSS
